text: Gabrielle Walsh (born May 10, 1989) is an American actress. She is best known for her roles as Marisol in the Paranormal Activity: The Marked Ones (2014), and as Jess in the science fiction thriller The Hive (2014). Walsh has also appeared on many television series such as Shameless, The Vampire Diaries, and From Dusk till Dawn: The Series. In 2020, she began voicing Emily in Close Enough, an adult animated comedy series on HBO Max. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Chicago Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors
